## 6. Communications

Communications Lead coordinates all internal and external messaging. Unauthorized statements are prohibited during Level 2+ events.

## 7. Recovery

Termination of crisis response requires Crisis Director approval, hot-wash within 48 hours, and documentation of unresolved issues.

